== What for

You can find demo of php and asp for alipay on its official forum, but you seldom can find a rails one.
I share my codes of alipay on rails, hoping I can help someone want it.

I developed it for an online render platform of my formal firm.

== How to use

To use it, first you should substitute "partner", "security_code" and "seller_email" which are still blank in this demo with your own ones.